{"tid":1672951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有一個youtuber因為發聲比人杯葛","createTime":"2019-10-24T11:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T13:54:51.000Z","uid":284872,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2531b2f6dc2ffffaaba5a045b3548c62dcec50","tid":1672951,"uid":284872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"果個就係有碗話碗啦 <br />\n其實佢地啲片畢嬲都高汁過香港好多youtuber好多班 <br />\n由其係果兩公婆 之後果個還擊真係一睇就知佢地咩level<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁佢作為飲食channel 都知佢地難做 但係響個幾禮拜前竟然為香港發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係依家佢地係比所謂嘅同路人、藍絲圍 <br />\n我地可唔可以支持返同路人 入去為佢地打氣呀 唔好比佢地灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B3_3NOOj-Hz/?igshid=9qhlxbhj8wi2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3_3NOOj-Hz%2F%3Figshid%3D9qhlxbhj8wi2&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=29db9946\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3_3NOOj-Hz%2F%3Figshid%3D9qhlxbhj8wi2&h=4d581994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B3_3NOOj-Hz/?igshid=9qhlxbhj8wi2</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B3_3NOOj-Hz/?igshid=9qhlxbhj8wi2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3_3NOOj-Hz%2F%3Figshid%3D9qhlxbhj8wi2&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=29db9946\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3_3NOOj-Hz%2F%3Figshid%3D9qhlxbhj8wi2&h=4d581994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B3_3NOOj-Hz/?igshid=9qhlxbhj8wi2</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B3_3NOOj-Hz/?igshid=9qhlxbhj8wi2\" data-sr-url=\"